    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-10-17T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-10-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="473"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d473">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.5017/10–1746: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Chargé in Brazil</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Daniels</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1946-10-17">October 17,
                            1946</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1360. <gloss target="#t_Depcirtel1">Depcirtel</gloss> Oct 17 unnumbered.<note
                        n="57" xml:id="d473fn57">Not printed.</note> Suspension today <gloss
                        target="#t_OPA1">OPA</gloss> coffee ceilings terminated Aug 14 Memo of
                    Understanding between Brazil and US. Dept accordingly delivering note to <gloss
                        target="#t_Braz1">Braz</gloss>
                    <gloss target="#t_Emb1">Emb</gloss> withdrawing request for October offering
                    500,000 bags coffee accordance that understanding. Please inform <gloss
                        target="#t_FonOff1">FonOff</gloss> this withdrawal.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
